1:14:46.278 --> 1:14:47.779
Where is he?

1:15:21.396 --> 1:15:22.397
Stop!

1:15:45.629 --> 1:15:48.131
Come on.
Come on, come on, come on.

1:16:05.440 --> 1:16:07.359
Come on,
come on, come on!

1:16:08.610 --> 1:16:10.404
You gotta be kidding me.

1:16:29.298 --> 1:16:31.300
Where are
the goddamn keys?

1:16:32.759 --> 1:16:33.760
Come on!

1:16:34.011 --> 1:16:35.345
Where are you?

1:16:52.779 --> 1:16:53.947
Come on...

1:17:44.748 --> 1:17:45.999
Asha, please!

1:17:47.125 --> 1:17:48.126
Help!

1:17:49.294 --> 1:17:50.295
Somebody help!

1:18:51.315 --> 1:18:52.316
Stop!

1:18:52.399 --> 1:18:53.400
Please!

1:18:53.609 --> 1:18:54.610
Stop!

1:19:15.506 --> 1:19:16.715
You're safe now.

1:19:18.550 --> 1:19:20.302
I won't let her hurt you.

1:19:38.904 --> 1:19:41.031
No! Somebody help!

1:19:41.198 --> 1:19:42.533
Please!

1:19:46.078 --> 1:19:47.079
No!

1:19:49.164 --> 1:19:51.041
Help, please!

1:19:56.255 --> 1:19:58.048
Please! Help!

1:21:27.554 --> 1:21:28.555
Amy?

1:21:30.641 --> 1:21:31.642
Amy?

1:21:38.815 --> 1:21:39.816
Amy?

1:21:40.817 --> 1:21:42.736
I'm hurt. I need your help.

1:22:17.062 --> 1:22:18.063
Amy!

1:22:18.939 --> 1:22:20.607
I kept having
the same nightmare.

1:22:21.149 --> 1:22:22.150
Over and over again.

1:22:23.151 --> 1:22:24.987
Amy was
missing for four days now.

1:22:25.487 --> 1:22:28.699
And the local police
were still searching for Navin.

1:22:30.951 --> 1:22:32.244
Nothing makes sense.

1:23:06.195 --> 1:23:07.196
Stop!

1:23:11.533 --> 1:23:14.077
Please, help us!
Please, open the door!

1:23:16.788 --> 1:23:18.165
Who would lock her in there?

1:23:18.373 --> 1:23:21.084
Wait, if you're here...
